name: Fantasymovies
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: fantasy movies
des:
This skill helps users to know the names of ten fantasy movies. People can get to know their names easily using this skill. This skill does not play or start a fantasy movie on screen . It will just inform the names of the ten fantasy movies.
After reaching HELP prompt, please say : "Tell me ten fantasy movies names " , to get the result.
Please listen to the device's instructions and follow the steps to get accurate result.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
